Text: Cookiesthought of you last night when we took the Russian Teacake cookies from Christmas out of the freezer and finished them Yumyum Im sending this from work because our computer at home is down The study is empty We had the carpet shampooed yesterday and the new furniture is supposed to be delivered next Tuesday We may put a card table in there tomorrow so we can connect the computer again That is the only room other than the kitchen that has a handy phone connection for the modem There is one in the bedroom but it is behind the dresser Im surprised at home much I miss it I noticed in the WSJ this morning that Enron is going to have some competition in online trading Ill be interested to see if the price is affected today See that is a good reason to connect that computer tonight Love Mother
